OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fthis evening and overnight with
OL,7,Fprolonged clear spells for most.
OL,8,FPatchy mist and fog reforming, though
OL,9,Fmore isolated than the previous night.
OL,10,FStrengthening breeze around the Moors.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSome sunshine possible in
OL,13,Fthe east, where feeling very mild.
OL,14,FTemperatures suppressed slightly in
OL,15,Fthe west as cloud thickens ahead of
OL,16,Frain arriving later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
